high_descs: Move across the room to the stove.
Pick up the round frying pan that is located on the front left side of the stove.
Turn to the left and move to the refrigerator.
Open the fridge and place the pan on the top shelf.  CLose the door and allow the pan to cool.  Remove the pan and close the door.
Carry the pan across the room back to the stove.
Place the pan on the back left side of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Cool a pan in the refrigerator to place on the back left burner of the stove.

high_descs: Walk a step forward and then turn left to face the stove top.
Pick up the frying pan on the bottom left burner.
Turn left and walk to the fridge so you are facing it.
Open the top compartment and place the frying pan on the top shelf to the right hand side and let it get cold before retrieving it.
Head over to the stove again so you are facing it.
Put the pan back on the stove but put it on the top left burner this time instead.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on the stove top.

high_descs: Turn and walk up to the stove on your left
Pick up the frying pan from the stove
Turn left and walk to the fridge
Put the pan into the fridge then remove it
Turn right and walk back over to the stove
Put the pan down on the back left stove burner
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled frying pan on the stove

high_descs: Proceed to stove, turn left to face stove.
Pick up pan from left bottom burner.
Turn left, proceed to fridge.  Turn right to face fridge.
Open fridge, put pan on top shelf to the right.  Close fridge.  Open fridge after six seconds, remove pan, close fridge.
Turn around, proceed to stove.
Turn toward stove, put pan on back left burner.
anns.task_desc: Put pan in fridge then on stove.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the stove
Pick up the pan from the front left burner
Turn to the left and go to just before the chair then turn to the right and go up to the fridge
Put the pan on the top shelf of the fridge then close the fridge, wait a bit then take the pan back out of the fridge
Turn around and go back to the stove
Put the pan on the back left burner
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the stove

high_descs: Walk forward and turn left towards the stove.
Grab the pan on the stove.
Turn left and walk across the room. Turn right towards the white cabinet.
Place the pan on the top shelf in the dishwasher.
Remove the pan from the dishwasher, turn around, then turn left and walk to the stove on the left side. Turn left to face the stove.
Place the pan on the back burner.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean pan on the stove
